Package ides.api.plugin.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DESElement
    Interface defining the required operations for an element in a discrete event system.
    DESEvent
    Defines an abstract event in a discrete-event system.
    DESEventSet
    A set of DESEvents.
    DESModel
    The interface for all models which IDES will handle.
    DESModelPublisher
    A publisher of DESModelMessages.
    DESModelSubscriber
    Subscriber to messages from a DESModel.
    DESModelType
    Descriptor for a DES model type.
    ParentModel
    Interface for DESModels which, in turn, contain other DESModels as child models.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DESModelMessage
    Message sent to the subscribers listening for updates of a DESModel.
    ModelManager
    The manager of model types available to IDES.
